sub_title: Data Quality Specialist and Leader, Data Entry, EMEA
summary:
International, self-motivated, responsible and hard working professional. Five years of work experience in one of the world's best executives search consulting firms. Adaptable to challenging situations. Works well both in a team environment as well as using own initiative. Able to work well under pressure and adhere to strict deadlines. 

Qualities:

Fluency in English, German and Polish
Excellent communications skills, both verbal and written
Analytical, quality and detail oriented, with ability to make decisions using own resoning and judgment
Well organized, good ability to set priorities and multitask
Strong planner who can arrange tasks and commit to predetermined deadlines in an organized manner against many conflicting priorities
Interpersomal skills to work well within a relatively unstructured environment
Computer literate with experience in internal databases, online research, Excel, Word processing, and PowerPoint
International experience and mind set
